{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act36side", "eventName": "泰拉飯", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DT-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "烤串與預言", "storyInfo": "奇爾查克在薩米做了一場古怪的夢，同時薩米的意志也告訴萊歐斯小隊要向北方去，並注意傳說中的獨眼巨人。這究竟意味著什麼呢？\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沙沙、沙沙——"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突如其來的聲響打斷了奇爾查克的夢境。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從來到這個陌生的地方，他總是會輕易地被周圍細小的動靜驚醒。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他來不及思考那個夢的含義，翻身而起，看向應該在守夜的萊歐斯的方向。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "40_g1_blackforest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所幸，這個平日裡總有些不正經的傢伙，在這種時候還是非常可靠的。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他已經喚醒了先西和瑪露希爾，並舉起了武器。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇爾查克，我們來吸引注意力，你來好好確認一下它們的狀況吧。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇爾查克發現，這只是一群小隊曾遭遇過多次的魔物，且對方還沒有注意到他們。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他稍微緩了口氣，把這個訊息帶回給了自己的同伴們。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來到這個名叫泰拉的世界後，他們已經見識了太多陌生的事物。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一行人交換了眼神，確認彼此做好了戰鬥準備。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我們上！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "必須在這未知的世界裡避開各種危險，無論是依靠那個羅德島，還是自己另找辦法，他們終究是要回去的，他想。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "40_g1_blackforest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……總算結束了。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我難得做了一個美夢呢，真浪費。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從你的睡相來看，你每天都在做美夢吧。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也沒有啦……等等，我的睡相很糟糕嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那倒沒有，我猜的。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，話說我們已經在這片黑森林裡走了好幾天了。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡真的有薩米的部族嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩米的本土部族都生活在一些奇怪的地方，而且大多不歡迎外人。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有那麼簡單就能找到。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得也是……唉，沒想到這裡居然這麼偏僻。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要去找雪祀的事可是瑪露希爾你提出來的，這就打退堂鼓了？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我提的時候又不知道這裡的環境這麼糟糕，還很可怕！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們剛到薩米的時候，那邊的條件明明還是很好的……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在那聽到了各種有趣的小故事，那裡有個叫“巴斯克星象”的小帳篷，裡面的人在占卜……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然後來我發現她是騙人的啦，那個水晶球就是她自己操控的，但她說的什麼“米諾斯傳說中一千個頭的怪物”還是蠻有趣的……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一個叫“米諾斯”的地方，有長著一千個頭的魔物！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我之前也聽傳聞說過有種很厲害的魔物，吃下什麼東西就可以獲得什麼樣的能力。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好啊，多夢幻啊……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就只對這種話題特別感興趣。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還是先想想怎麼找到雪祀吧，我真的走不動了……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "強大的人會適應環境，瑪露希爾。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心，也不需要適應這樣的環境，我可不想多來這樣的地方。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣思考會阻礙你成長的。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對老夫而言，比起人為建造的街道，還是這樣的地方更好。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不是說不找雪祀了……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，那個占卜師說去了黑森林就能找到他們，結果這不是什麼都沒有嗎！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡又潮濕又沒有光樹木又多魔物還多補給又快吃完了你們一定又要吃魔物了。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊歐斯，你怎麼看？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯——這片黑森林的魔物和我們之前遇到的並沒有太大不同，我還以為能看到一些稀奇的魔物。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森林往往掩藏著許多秘密，只是我們還不瞭解它。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與其說又要吃了，不如說，那邊那兩個已經在割剛才打倒的魔物的肉了。太好了，瑪露希爾，你又有口福了。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不要我不要我不要！！！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$leaveshake", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼又來了！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我來晚了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是……？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊歐斯，你能不能不要一隻手握著你那沾血的劍用手背擦臉，一隻手提著魔物的肉跟人打招呼——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，沒關係的。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比這更刺激的場景我也經常見到。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們可以叫我橡杯，我是一名薩滿學徒。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一群羽獸告知了我你們的處境，於是我趕了過來。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，就算我不來，你們應該也能處理好。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#9$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢，請不用擔心，我沒有惡意，也不想惹麻煩，既然各位沒有事，那我就不打擾——", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你剛才說，你是薩滿學徒？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們踏入這片黑森林，是希望找到薩米部族中的雪祀，為我們占卜回家的道路，或是……至少幫我們找到羅德島的位置。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回家？", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#6$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，由於一些原因，我們不知道該怎麼回家。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於羅德島，有人告訴我們，可以尋求一個叫羅德島的地方的幫助，但我們一直找不到它的位置。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#6$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "南邊有許多急著想要“引導”他人的傢伙。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#6$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，這個我們已經體驗過了，“巴斯克星象”。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總而言之，外來者對薩米的占卜經常會有你們這樣的誤解。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們很少為他人的未來、他人的願望而占卜，我們的占卜只為自己的生存。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只會在必要的時候請求薩米的意志引導我們。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們祈求薩米告知我們未來之中潛藏的危險並做出準備，但是在那之外，我們依照自然的法則生活。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自然的法則？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像各位現在正在做的一樣。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狩獵，被狩獵；活著進食，死了變食物。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫果然喜歡這裡。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我有個問題。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請說。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你口中的薩米，會托夢給人嗎？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……雖然我沒有遇到過，但是藉由這種方式獲得啟示並不是沒有可能。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟誰也說不清自己的夢究竟是真是假。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你作了預知夢嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒有。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神秘兮兮的……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，你不願意帶我們去找雪祀嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……與其說不願意，我主要是覺得有點麻煩……", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#8$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，如果你們真的去找其他部族的薩滿，可能會直接被轟出去。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#8$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……有沒有什麼省時又省力的辦法呢——", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，旁邊的這棵樹上……掉下來了兩塊樹皮？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樹皮上怎麼有奇怪的符文……我看不懂這些符文。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？可以讓我看一看嗎？", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然，這是薩米的指引……", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩米啊，感謝你，你可是幫我省了不少的力氣。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樹皮是……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你手中的兩塊樹皮，是密文板，它們所代表的，正是薩米的意志。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩滿們進行占卜的方式多種多樣，但時不時地，薩米也會像這樣主動投來視線。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#9$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也太巧了。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我有時候也這麼想。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是反過來想，要是你們抱著兩塊樹皮卻一直找不到人為你們解讀，不是更煩惱嗎？", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#10$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你這個薩滿學徒怎麼給人感覺這麼隨意，薩滿一般不應該是更加嚴肅的人嗎？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也拿這個問題問過我的師父，他的回答是連續兩天用我的角當酒杯，我就再也不敢問了。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能告訴我們樹皮上寫了什麼嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一塊……“北方”？", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意思是，我們應該往北走？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們已經走在向北的道路上了，薩米卻依然給出了“北方”。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，祂可能想讓你們去更北的地方。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更北？奇爾查克，那裡有什麼？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地圖上寫著，出了黑森林，就是薩米的核心林地，再往北，是被大雪覆蓋的群山，以及無盡冰原。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思，薩米該不會要我們去無盡冰原吧？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩米的意志往往只會給出一個模糊的意象。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但要我說，我的直覺告訴我，你是對的。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無盡冰原？我稍微打聽了一下都知道那是有去無回的地方啊。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你們剛才也說了，你們不知道回家的路。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未知的路藏在無人生還之所，不是剛好嗎？", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#10$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一塊……“隱者”，哈哈，這可有意思了。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“隱者”又是什麼？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“隱者”可以指許多東西……但是，如果是“北方”加上“隱者”，那麼，答案幾乎只有一個——", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨眼巨人。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？！", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#7$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道獨眼巨人？", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#4$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……收集情報的時候聽到過這個名字。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是什麼魔物嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……不是，他們是薩卡茲特殊的一支。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#8$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們擁有和薩米人的占卜截然不同的，預知未來的方法。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#5$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，他們隱居在北方的群山之中。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#5$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩塊密文板結合起來，薩米應該是想要告訴你們——", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#2$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_964_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去北方尋求獨眼巨人的幫助，他們會協助你們找到回家的路。", "name": "橡杯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_964_1#5$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我打算試一試。各位，你們覺得呢？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然有能夠直接回去的方法，老夫認為值得嘗試。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……如果真的有能夠回去的方法，我也不反對就是了。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇爾查克呢？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們三個人都同意了，問我的意見有意義嗎？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然有，畢竟你是隊伍的一員。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那我就直說了。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不同意。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "40_g1_blackforest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇爾查克，你不相信橡杯先生說的話嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#5$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是不相信他，這個人說的話不像是假的，我看得出來。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#3$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼不同意？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "預言也好，占卜也好，你們都太容易相信這種東西了。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是人家算計好了，就是要在那個地方給你掉兩塊樹皮下來，你們現在不就又受騙了嗎？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇爾查克說得有道理，不過，我覺得再往北方走一走也沒有壞處。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是遇到別的薩滿，請他再幫我們解讀一下就知道橡杯有沒有在騙我們了。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經在這個世界待了相當長一段時間了，任何能夠回去的方法，我都不想錯過。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好吧。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起這個，我怎麼總感覺我們一直在同一個地方繞來繞去？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們剛才真的沒有經過這裡嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……老夫有做標記，我們應該一直在前進。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇爾查克，怎麼了？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先西說得沒錯，但是，這裡的地形給我一種很不自然的感覺。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像，地形本身在發生變化一樣……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像迷宮裡那樣？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，有點類似，只是，迷宮裡不斷變化的是機關，而這裡發生改變的……是整片森林。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們看，前面有一座懸崖，我先過去看一看附近的地形。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$a_bat_buildingshaking_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.5, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼聲音？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "循著震動的方向望去，四人看到了一頭體格非常健壯的公牛外形的魔物。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——當然，如今他們已經學會了用“角獸”去稱呼牠。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這樣的森林中，照理說出現什麼生物都不奇怪，但這頭角獸還是吸引了四個人的目光……原因無他——"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一張黑色的臉……黑色？不，那是虛空，無垠的虛空。"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們第一時間聯想到的，是夜晚抬頭時看到的銀河。"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一頭牛的臉上長著一片虛空——這個現實讓他們感到了不可置信。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而更讓他們震撼的是，這片虛空的正中，有一個圓。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個完美到讓人不安的圓。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個比周圍的虛空還要黑暗的圓。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比黑夜更黑，比虛空更深邃。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個圓是在發光嗎？"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是的，這是一個洞，一切的光都被這個洞吸收了，以至於它甚至看起來像是在發光。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以至於——它比光還要奪目。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種魔物……好奇怪。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠臉上的這片虛空似乎不是生物性的。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好有趣，好想研究看看！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#11$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（吼叫）", "name": "被污染的角獸"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠好像生氣了！", "name": "奇爾查克"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠的身體上有傷口，是武器的傷口……有人先激怒了牠，牠把我們也當成敵人了！", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃我一斧！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（吃痛的吼叫）", "name": "被污染的角獸"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pcknmrn", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.5}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2013_cerber_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背著很多武器的女孩？！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟糕，懸崖要塌了！奇爾查克！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊歐斯立刻向著已經來到懸崖邊的奇爾查克跑去，然而，還是晚了一步。"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使奇爾查克同樣盡力向著回去的方向奔跑跳躍，萊歐斯終究還是沒有抓住他的手，只能眼睜睜看著奇爾查克摔下懸崖。"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}